What is HMI?
----------------

HMI is a free Qt-based implementation of a Human Machine Interface application.
A graphical user interface allows easy manipulation of standard cheese coocking
machine over serial line. HMI also includes a monitor for logging all done jobs
on a MySql Database.



Requirements
------------

* Qt4
* GCC



Building
--------

See INSTALL for information on how to build QModBus.



